9:["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","main",null,{"className":"pb-16 text-brand-ink","children":["$","section",null,{"className":"px-4 py-12 sm:py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"page-shell","children":["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs sm:text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-brand-ink/50","children":"Guide / 修正申报"}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold leading-tight","children":"2026 Form 8843 填错了/寄早了？留学生修正申报 (Amended Return) 全攻略(附 PDF 下载)"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-6 text-lg text-brand-ink/80 leading-relaxed","children":["$","p",null,{"children":"很多同学发现自己 8843 寄早了，是因为还没搞清楚自己到底属于 Resident 还是 Non-resident。 在开始修正（Amend）之前，请先用下方工具确认你的 2026 报税身份："}]}],["$","$Lc",null,{}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-pink max-w-none mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"为什么“寄早了”也需要修正？（常见场景：未等 1042-S 寄达）"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":["在 2026 报税季，很多同学在 2 月份就匆匆寄出了 Form 8843。 然而，到了 3 月份才收到学校寄来的 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"1042-S 表格"}],"（涉及奖学金或 Treaty 免税）。 如果你已经寄出了 8843 却忘了附上 1040-NR 或 1042-S，这会导致你的收入报告不完整。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7 mt-4","children":"此外，如果你在 OPT 期间误把自己报成了 Resident（居民），漏掉了 8843， 这份漏掉的表可能会在未来成为你身份记录中的一个断点，必须通过修正申报来补齐。"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"如何提交 Amended Return？修正 Form 8843 的具体步骤"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 mb-4","children":["修正申报通常涉及 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"Form 1040-X"}],"。虽然 8843 本身不是税表，但它经常需要配合修正后的税表一起寄送。"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"soft-card !bg-white border border-brand-pink/20","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep","children":"步骤 1：下载并填写 Form 1040-X"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-brand-ink/70 mt-2","children":"在 1040-X 的 Explanation 部分，明确说明你是因为“漏交 Form 8843”或“重新判定 Non-resident 身份”而进行修正。"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"soft-card !bg-white border border-brand-pink/20","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep","children":"步骤 2：重新填写一份完整的 Form 8843"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-brand-ink/80 mt-2","children":["在新的 8843 表格顶部用红笔或黑色加粗字体标注：",["$","strong",null,{"children":"“AMENDED”"}],"。确保所有勾选项与你最新的身份判定一致。"]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"soft-card !bg-white border border-brand-pink/20","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-brand-pinkdeep","children":"步骤 3：组合寄送"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-brand-ink/80 mt-2","children":"将 1040-X、全新的 8843、以及原始申报的副本装在一起，邮寄至 IRS 修正申报专用地址。"}]]}]]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold mt-12 mb-6 text-brand-ink","children":"填错 8843 会影响未来的 H1B 或绿卡申请吗？"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7","children":["答案是：",["$","strong",null,{"children":"可能会"}],"。虽然 Form 8843 不直接涉及税金，但它是你维持“合法非居民”税务身份的唯一书面声明。 如果你连续多年漏交、或者在 OPT 期间因为填错 8843/1040 导致多拿了不该拿的 Standard Deduction， 在 H1B 审计或绿卡面试中，面试官可能会质疑你的税务合规性。"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-brand-ink/75 leading-7 mt-4","children":["好消息是，IRS 允许在 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"3 年法定追诉期"}]," 内进行合规修正。只要你主动提交了 Amended Return， 这种主动修正的行为通常会被视为“Good Faith Error Correction”，极大地降低了审计风险。"]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 rounded-[28px] border border-brand-pink/40 bg-white/95 p-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(244,185,200,0.3)]","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-brand-ink","children":"修正必备工具包"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"soft-card !bg-brand-pink/5","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold mb-2","children":"官方表格预览"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-brand-ink/70 mb-4","children":"修正申报